[SPEAKER_00] neko ima cigarete,

1236
01:28:28,380 --> 01:28:29,060
[SPEAKER_00] neko ima kocku,

1237
01:28:29,060 --> 01:28:29,779
[SPEAKER_00] neko ima šećer,

1238
01:28:29,779 --> 01:28:30,840
[SPEAKER_00] evo mene imam šećer.

1239
01:28:30,840 --> 01:28:32,180
[SPEAKER_00] I cigarete.

1240
01:28:32,180 --> 01:28:33,899
[SPEAKER_00] Nemam kocku,

